@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_wkulsi(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((tmp / wp.sin(v0 + 0.02)) / wp.exp((v2 + 0.74 / v2 + 0.78)))
    v0 = ((wp.exp(v1 + 0.96) * wp.sin(v0 + 0.59)) + wp.cos(v1))
    v1 = wp.exp((wp.exp(v1 + 0.41) * 0.96))
    v0 = wp.sin(0.82)
    v1 = wp.cos(v1)
    data[tid] = v0
